entries.quest_dock_d: Once you have found some more information that command can use against the Rebels, dock with the scout and transfer that information to your vessel.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Disable and inspect the scout for any more data that can be used by command.
entries.quest_inspect_t: Inspect the Rebel Advanced Recon Fighter
entries.quest_location_d: Intelligence has located another Rebel Advanced Recon fighter in the Endor system. Travel to the supplied navigation waypoint in order to find the second scout.
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! Enemy ships detected incoming at attack speeds. Take evasive action immediately. Destroy all incoming fighters.
entries.title: Endor System: Inspect Another Rebel Advanced Recon Fighter
entries.title_d: Travel to the Endor system and inspect another Rebel Advanced Recon fighter. Command needs more details as to the Rebel operation in the system. Intelligence has a lock on the location of another Rebel Advanced Recon fighter that seems to be a good target.
